name: Exam Professor
overview:
Want to publish exams online? We’ve got the answer!

Exam Professor is a web-based tool that allows you to build, embed, and sell access to your own exams, tests or quizzes (or drill and practice) quickly and easily. From professors setting up their final exam to small businesses training employees, Exam Professor is a breeze to use.

With Exam Professor you can embed individual exams or the entire student interface, and customize the color and logo to match your site. It is used by educators, non-profits, businesses, and other professionals who need an easy way to publish exams, tests, and quizzes online quickly.
